- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the applicability of nested weighted automata in several domains, which may involve data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a less likely category, but possible as the paper mentions the use of nested weighted automata in decision-making and optimization problems, which are topics related to AI.
